name: The Sister I Never Had - 2
description:
We shined together at our best
We understood each other at our worst
You’re the sister I never had
We had our priorities but hanged out at Friday nights
We had our differences and fights but kept our friendship tight
You’re the sister I never had
When we got our hearts broken, we cried together
When we had our little successes, we both win
You’re the sister I never had
You fought for me when I was weak
You’re the greatest fan and supporter that I had
You protected my happiness with an armory
Now it’s my time to protect yours, the happiness of the sister I never had.

by Jovierose
